text: Ryan Longwell (born August 16, 1974Ryan Longwell #8: Bio. NFL Players.com. Retrieved December 2, 2007.) was an NFL kicker from 1997-2012. He went to college in California. He played for the Green Bay Packers and the Minnesota Vikings.
